Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Un personatge misteriós, en Komakichi Kurataya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:06.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"li ha enviat una carta a en Kogoro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,per dir-li que li ha d'entregar\Nun tresor familiar."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La Ran i jo hem decidit\Nacompanyar-lo a Yamaguchi."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però la policia ha confós en Kogoro\Namb el còmplice d'un lladre
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i l'ha detingut."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Hem descobert\Nque Komakichi Kurataya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"és el pseudònim d'un lladre\Nque va robar unes monedes antigues
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,valorades\Nen centenars de milions de iens."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:28.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Afortunadament, en Kogoro ha quedat\Nen llibertat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:31.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,gràcies a l'Asuka Natsume,\Nperiodista d'un diari digital."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però resulta que va ser ella,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,qui li va enviar la carta fent-se\Npassar per en Komakichi Kurataya."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'Asuka li volia encarregar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que investigués el robatori\Nde les monedes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,però ho havia de fer sense cridar\Nl'atenció del culpable."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Seguint una possible pista,\Nhem sortit de Yamaguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:51.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i hem anat a una altra ciutat,\NHagi."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Tot d'una..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.92,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Ostres, això és el paradís!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha! Apa, ja podem marxar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.72,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ran, ajupe't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.88,White,,0,0,0,,Ep, això no es toca!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.44,White,,0,0,0,,Ei, què fa...? Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.28,White,,0,0,0,,Ui...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Amagueu-vos aquí al darrere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.64,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què ha sigut això? Un tret?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.32,White,,0,0,0,,Estàs bé, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.92,White,,0,0,0,,S'ha escapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Em sembla que ara en Komakichi Kurataya vol matar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,en Kogoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:27.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Comença un nou dia\Namb un sol esplèndid."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"És l'hora de l'amor\Ni dels misteris."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:31.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un pistoler vol matar en Kogoro."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"On ens portarà el tresor antic\Nde la Restauració?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:39.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:42.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,WAKE UP!! Me wo samashite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kizukareru mae ni tobidashite ikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsumo urusai hito
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,nemutchaeba mou jamamono wa inai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mondai darake no\Nmachi de Knock Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Uchikowasu tameiki to souon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:04.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yuku hito no kage yatsu wo Rock On!\NSusumu ude no tokei wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kauntodaun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kowase Bad Day! Everything OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hashiridase kimi no te wo totte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:20.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Zutto futari\Nde kono machi ni mou goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Asu e Go Now. Everything OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:26.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mayou made yukeru tokoro e.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sakebu kokoro de\N"I just wanna get the truth!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:35.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Donna kotoba mo mou iranai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:42.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Koko ni kotae wa nai,\Ntsukisusumu On My Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kowase Bad Day! Everything OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mayou made yukeru tokoro e.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sakebu kokoro de...\NI just wanna get the truth!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,(Go, go, go, go!) Get the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,(Go, go, go, go!) Get the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:13.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La gira dels misteris: la Revolució Bakumatsu (part de Hagi)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:26.44,White,,0,0,0,,(càmera, dispara: clac)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què fas, pare?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.52,White,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.28,White,,0,0,0,,Me'n vaig. Fa massa estona\Nque estem de braços plegats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ja, però on vols anar?\NPensa que encara no hem declarat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,Vaig penjar el vídeo al portal\Nde notícies de l'Asuka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.72,White,,0,0,0,,perquè ella tenia por\Nque el culpable la matés
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.80,White,,0,0,0,,i vaig pensar\Nque la tranquil·litzaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.68,White,,0,0,0,,però ara el culpable s'ho ha pres\Ncom una provocació.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.76,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.76,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Llavors...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:54.12,White,,0,0,0,,L'Asuka no està fora de perill,\Nella també està amenaçada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Ran, hauríem d'avisar l'Asuka com més aviat millor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.96,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ah. Hola, Asuka, soc la Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.44,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Eh? No res. M'ha saltat\Nel contestador.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.40,White,,0,0,0,,Vinga, no podem perdre temps.\NAnem a veure si la trobem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.52,White,,0,0,0,,Una altra vegada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.12,White,,0,0,0,,On es pensa que va?\NQue no veu que el volen matar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.20,White,,0,0,0,,Ja. I quin problema hi ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.04,White,,0,0,0,,Sàpiga que nosaltres li podem\Ngarantir la seguretat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.64,White,,0,0,0,,Dit d'una altra manera:\Nel podem protegir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.36,White,,0,0,0,,No cal, gràcies. No em fa cap falta,\Nque em protegeixin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.80,White,,0,0,0,,Som-hi, Ran. Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.24,White,,0,0,0,,Punyeta, que pesats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.12,White,,0,0,0,,-No surti del cotxe, entesos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:46.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Escolta, pare, com ens ho farem,\Nper avisar l'Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.28,White,,0,0,0,,No pateixis.\NEsperarem que estiguin distrets i...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(home) Inspector Takajo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.76,White,,0,0,0,,Mm? Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.68,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos. Jo mateix em posaré\Nen contacte amb la central.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.76,White,,0,0,0,,Vosaltres ocupeu-vos dels...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.96,White,,0,0,0,,Merda! El detectiu de pacotilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Què feu aquí aturats? Busqueu-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Asuka) Vet aquí el forn\Nde reverber de Hagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.88,White,,0,0,0,,vestigi de la Revolució Industrial Meiji del Japó
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.96,White,,0,0,0,,i patrimoni de la humanitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.20,White,,0,0,0,,Durant l'època feudal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.00,White,,0,0,0,,els forns de reverber es feien\Nservir per fondre metall
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.12,White,,0,0,0,,i refinar bales de canó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,Al segle XIX, els joves\Ndel domini feudal de Choshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.84,White,,0,0,0,,van dedicar cos i ànima a construir\Naquests forns emblemàtics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.20,White,,0,0,0,,Al final, però, els seus esforços\Ni dedicació...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.28,White,,0,0,0,,no van donar el fruit que esperaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.64,White,,0,0,0,,Encara ara es nota la passió\Ndels joves patriotes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.52,White,,0,0,0,,de la Revolució Bakumatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.00,White,,0,0,0,,que es van esforçar de valent\Nper fer realitat un somni.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.72,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.80,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.28,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: to de trucada)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Asuka, soc jo. Està bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.84,White,,0,0,0,,-"Hola, soc l'Asuka."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.24,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, senyor Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.40,White,,0,0,0,,Com diu? Sí, estic bé...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.12,White,,0,0,0,,-"Ha passat alguna cosa?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Quin descans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.12,White,,0,0,0,,La veritat és que sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.92,White,,0,0,0,,Fa una estona m'han disparat\Namb una pistola al mig del carrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.40,White,,0,0,0,,Amb una pistola?!\NPerò li han fet mal? Està bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.76,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Per sort, estic bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.80,White,,0,0,0,,Estic segur que l'home que m'ha disparat era en Komakichi Kurataya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.96,White,,0,0,0,,En Komakichi Kurataya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.20,White,,0,0,0,,Asuka, vostè també corre perill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.88,White,,0,0,0,,-"És al forn de reverber, oi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.84,White,,0,0,0,,Sí... Soc a l'aparcament,\Nal peu de les escales.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.64,White,,0,0,0,,"Entesos. Vinc de seguida.\NNo es mogui, d'acord?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:41.52,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord, l'espero.\NAfanyi's, sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.16,White,,0,0,0,,Mm! Mm! Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm! Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.60,White,,0,0,0,,-"Què ha passat? Asuka! Asuka!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.52,White,,0,0,0,,"Passa res, Asuka?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.56,White,,0,0,0,,"Sisplau, contesti. Asuka! Asuka!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:01.48,White,,0,0,0,,Asuka..., on és?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.92,White,,0,0,0,,Asukaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Si ens sent, respongui, sisplau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.08,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,És el mòbil de l'Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.44,White,,0,0,0,,Això és...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.56,White,,0,0,0,,Una videotrucada del senyor Takarada?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.00,White,,0,0,0,,"Ostres. I l'Asuka?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.24,White,,0,0,0,,-"Eh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyor Takarada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.12,White,,0,0,0,,No sé on és, acabo de descobrir\Nque l'han segrestat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.00,White,,0,0,0,,"No pot ser."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.84,White,,0,0,0,,Per telèfon m'ha dit que era\Na l'aparcament del forn de reverber,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:36.36,White,,0,0,0,,però quan hi hem arribat només\Nhem trobat el seu mòbil a terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.60,White,,0,0,0,,-"Senyor Mouri..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.64,White,,0,0,0,,"Em fa l'efecte que això ha sigut\Ncosa del senyor Fujiki."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.96,White,,0,0,0,,Aquell advocat, vol dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.84,White,,0,0,0,,"L'Asuka sospitava que era ell
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.00,White,,0,0,0,,qui s'amagava darrere la identitat d'en Komakichi Kurataya."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:53.60,White,,0,0,0,,Si això fos cert, on creu\Nque se la deu haver emportat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.40,White,,0,0,0,,"No en tinc ni idea,\Nperò ella em va explicar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.84,White,,0,0,0,,"que havia quedat amb en Fujiki\Ndiverses vegades
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.88,White,,0,0,0,,i que ell sempre li proposava\Nque es trobessin al parc Shizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Al parc Shizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.56,White,,0,0,0,,"És on hi ha les ruïnes\Ndel castell de Hagi."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.80,White,,0,0,0,,"Estan envoltades per un fossat\Ni un mur de pedra."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:15.16,White,,0,0,0,,"Ella creia que en Fujiki hi amagava les monedes que m'havia robat."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.68,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors, l'Asuka podria ser allà?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.48,White,,0,0,0,,"Ara mateix vinc\Na trobar-me amb vostè."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.88,White,,0,0,0,,"Però trigaré una hora ben bona\Na arribar a Hagi amb cotxe."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.60,White,,0,0,0,,Entesos, intentarem arribar-hi\Naixí que puguem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "No ho entenc."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Com és que a en Kogoro\Nli ha disparat amb una pistola
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i a l'Asuka no?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Oh... Potser només li ha disparat\Nper espantar-lo."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Llavors...,\Nper què ha segrestat l'Asuka?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Perquè a ella sí que la vol matar?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I on la deu haver portat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ha de ser un lloc on se'n pugui\Ndesempallegar sense testimonis."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.60,White,,0,0,0,,L'antiga moneda anomenada "koban" conté gairebé un 90% d'or.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.76,White,,0,0,0,,És possible que les hagin fos\Ni les hagin transformat en lingots
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.64,White,,0,0,0,,per poder vendre l'or\Namb molta més facilitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "No deu voler...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ei, Ran! Deixa'm veure\Nel mòbil de l'Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He de veure els vídeos antics\Ndel seu portal de notícies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.40,White,,0,0,0,,"Per mi, els forns de reverber\Nde Hagi són un lloc de poder."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.76,White,,0,0,0,,(Asuka) "Un lloc de poder?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.48,White,,0,0,0,,"Són unes construccions\Nque els senyors feudals de Choshu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.56,White,,0,0,0,,van intentar aixecar\Nsense disseny previ."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.44,White,,0,0,0,,"Quan surto a passejar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.04,White,,0,0,0,,"vinc aquí tot sovint per sentir\Nel poder d'aquells homes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.12,White,,0,0,0,,que es van enfrontar\Na tantes dificultats."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Asuka) "Ah...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.48,White,,0,0,0,,"La foneria que vostè fa servir\Nés molt a prop d'aquí."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,White,,0,0,0,,-"Sí."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.56,White,,0,0,0,,-"Oi, senyor Fukuhara?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh? Aturi's, sisplau. He de baixar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.52,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Ei, què fas, marrec?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vostè i la Ran continuïn\Ncap al parc Shizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Vindré després,\Nquan hagi comprovat una cosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:01.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ei! On vas? Què dius\Nque vols comprovar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.40,White,,0,0,0,,Vigila, ajupe't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.96,White,,0,0,0,,La policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.72,White,,0,0,0,,Uh! Bufa, ha anat de ben poc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Quina ràbia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.88,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Hem d'actuar com si haguéssim fet\Nalguna cosa mal feta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.16,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que ens amaguem,\Nperquè aquell inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sàpiga que nosaltres li podem\Ngarantir la seguretat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.76,White,,0,0,0,,Dit d'una altra manera:\Nel podem protegir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.04,White,,0,0,0,,Mm? Un moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.08,White,,0,0,0,,Aquesta ciutat no entra dins\Nla seva jurisdicció.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.24,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors, per què han vingut\Na investigar, quan m'han disparat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.56,White,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "I si aquell carallot...\Nfos en Komakichi Kurataya?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.44,White,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "On és?\NHe de trobar la foneria! Oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"És allà!\NEspero arribar-hi a temps!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.80,White,,0,0,0,,(gemega)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ah..., ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.20,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.80,White,,0,0,0,,Oh... Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.44,White,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Merda! He d'aturar la cinta\Nde seguida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.12,White,,0,0,0,,Conan, afanya't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.64,White,,0,0,0,,Atura-la, de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Endavaaant...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.44,White,,0,0,0,,-(màquina: clac)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Uf! He arribat a temps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,Espera'm aquí, entesos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:41.68,White,,0,0,0,,Recorda que porta una pistola.\NPassi el que passi, no em segueixis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.44,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: ring)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.20,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: ring)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Conan! On ets, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:52.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hola, Ran. Soc amb l'Asuka.\NL'he trobat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Molt bé. I tu? On és el teu pare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,"De debò? Espero que estigui bé."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,L'he perdut de vista, acaba d'entrar tot sol al parc Shizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.76,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.44,White,,0,0,0,,És el senyor Fujiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.72,White,,0,0,0,,I el carallot de l'inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.24,White,,0,0,0,,Estaven conxorxats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.52,White,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.56,White,,0,0,0,,(tret: ressona)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,No et moguis...,\Ndetectiu de pacotilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.84,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Takajo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.92,White,,0,0,0,,Sabia que eres tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.08,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,-No moguis ni un dit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,Eh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.56,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Punyeta! Ara s'ha escapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Ei..., ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.08,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs... doncs jo em pensava\Nque m'apuntaves a mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.92,White,,0,0,0,,A tu? Per què carai\Nt'hauria de disparar, a tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.32,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.84,White,,0,0,0,,Algú t'apuntava amb una pistola\Ndes d'aquests arbustos d'aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Com?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:45.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Per tant, el culpable és...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:45.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Ha abandonat l'arma i ha fugit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.72,White,,0,0,0,,Digui'm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ei, tu, marrec!\NDigue'm ara mateix on ets i què fas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh? Què t'empatolles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.24,White,,0,0,0,,Em sap greu arribar tan tard,\Nsenyor Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.80,White,,0,0,0,,L'esperàvem, senyor Takarada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.68,White,,0,0,0,,Tenia raó quan m'ha dit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.92,White,,0,0,0,,que es triga més d'una hora a venir\Namb cotxe des de Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, oh, i tant. Però tant se val.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.52,White,,0,0,0,,I l'Asuka? L'han trobat o què? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.36,White,,0,0,0,,Què... què hi fan, aquí,\Nla policia i el senyor Fujiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.04,White,,0,0,0,,Què... què vol dir, això?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyor Takarada...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.32,White,,0,0,0,,¿Ho sabia, que el senyor Fujiki era l'advocat d'en Yuichi Fukuhara,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.40,White,,0,0,0,,l'home condemnat pel robatori\Nde les monedes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.48,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.16,White,,0,0,0,,El senyor Fukuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.96,White,,0,0,0,,té motius per sospitar que vostè podria ser en Komakichi Kurataya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.44,White,,0,0,0,,Però... com vol que jo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:48.48,White,,0,0,0,,Va dir que no estava d'acord\Namb el testament del seu difunt pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.64,White,,0,0,0,,La seva voluntat era\Nque les obres d'art i antiguitats
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.84,White,,0,0,0,,guardades al magatzem de la cafeteria
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.92,White,,0,0,0,,es donessin a institucions locals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.04,White,,0,0,0,,Per això va decidir robar\Nla col·lecció de monedes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.16,White,,0,0,0,,Si les fonia\Ni les convertia en lingots d'or,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.40,White,,0,0,0,,les podria vendre\Ni treure'n una fortuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.80,White,,0,0,0,,Para el carro! No tens cap prova\Nque jo sigui l'home que busqueu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.44,White,,0,0,0,,No en tinc cap prova.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.72,White,,0,0,0,,Però estic convençut que,\Nd'alguna manera,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.96,White,,0,0,0,,es va adonar que la senyoreta Asuka\Ncomençava a sospitar de vostè.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, per això l'ha segrestat i\Nha intentat fer-la callar per sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:24.68,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector, oi que vostè no se\Nles creu, totes aquestes ximpleries?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.76,White,,0,0,0,,El lladre em va disparar al braç!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.32,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.84,White,,0,0,0,,Però la bala amb prou feines\Nli va fregar el braç esquerre,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.92,White,,0,0,0,,era una ferida molt superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.20,White,,0,0,0,,És molt probable\Nque es disparés vostè mateix
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.28,White,,0,0,0,,per fer-se passar per la víctima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,Qui-quina bestiesa!\NNo ho poden demostrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(Kogoro) En tenim una prova.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:49.00,White,,0,0,0,,-No tinc ni idea de què vol dir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:49.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Vostè m'ha disparat dues vegades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.88,White,,0,0,0,,La primera vegada ha sigut\Nfa una hora i mitja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.20,White,,0,0,0,,I fa una hora m'ha disparat\Nper segona vegada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.88,White,,0,0,0,,Diguin el que vulguin,\Nperò jo tinc coartada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.72,White,,0,0,0,,Acabo d'arribar a Hagi,\Nja ho han vist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.48,White,,0,0,0,,I no m'he mogut de Yamaguchi\Nfins ara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:13.08,White,,0,0,0,,Vostè mateix m'ha vist al garatge\Nde casa meva, quan li he trucat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.80,White,,0,0,0,,Segur, que era a casa seva,\Nquan li he agafat la videotrucada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.28,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:21.20,White,,0,0,0,,És veritat que darrere seu hi tenia un cotxe esportiu molt cridaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:24.96,White,,0,0,0,,Així, qualsevol hauria pensat\Nque parlava des del seu garatge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.24,White,,0,0,0,,No sé què vol dir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.64,White,,0,0,0,,Quan el va gravar\Namb la seva càmera web,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.48,White,,0,0,0,,en Komakichi Kurataya sortia\Ndisfressat de milicià.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:36.12,White,,0,0,0,,Una roba cridanera desvia l'atenció\Nde la persona que la porta,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,o sigui, el culpable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:41.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ha fet servir la mateixa tècnica\Nper fer-nos creure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:43.40,White,,0,0,0,,que parlava des del garatge\Nde casa seva:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,desviar l'atenció\Namb un cotxe ben cridaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.64,White,,0,0,0,,Mm. I on es pensa que era,\Nsi no era al garatge de casa meva?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què, Conan, estàs preparat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:58.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Giro la pantalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:58.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Mm-hm. Comencem quan vulguis."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Hola, senyor Takarada."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:06.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ha dit que els paletes de l'edifici del costat de la cafeteria
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,feien soroll\Ndes del matí fins al vespre."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però quan hem parlat amb vostè\Nper telèfon fa una estona,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,no se sentia res de res."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Me n'he adonat gràcies a això."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He descobert\Nque no era al seu garatge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,sinó que parlava\Ndes de dins d'un camió."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ho ha preparat tot per fer veure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:29.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que ens trucava\Ndes del garatge de casa seva."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però, en realitat, ja feia estona\Nque havia arribat a Hagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i parlava des de dins del camió."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.28,White,,0,0,0,,"Ostres. I l'Asuka?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.56,White,,0,0,0,,Senyor Takarada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.52,White,,0,0,0,,No sé on és, acabo de descobrir\Nque l'han segrestat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,"No pot ser."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:48.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I també és aquí on ha portat l'Asuka quan l'ha segrestat."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.00,White,,0,0,0,,"Senyor Takarada..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.08,White,,0,0,0,,"Jo sabia que en Komakichi Kurataya,\Nel lladre...,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.60,White,,0,0,0,,...era vostè."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.68,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.76,White,,0,0,0,,Que no s'escapi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.12,White,,0,0,0,,-(rodes: xerriquen)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh? Oh, merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.72,White,,0,0,0,,(monedes, dringadissa: cling-cling)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,("Kamikaze express", Takuto)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aa kasumi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:45.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,nobashita ude ga\Nsukoshi furuete iru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:52.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aa fuan to kouyoukan\Nissho kuta ni shite
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:55.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,nami wa yurameite ita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:20:00.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mirai wa sou fuu\Nwo kiru mae no mae,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:05.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,dekiagatte sae inai genzairyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:11.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Madamada agakeru\Nkoko kara kakerun datte
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:15.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no kimi no hitokoe\Nde subete hajimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:22.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichi ni no san de aizu shite\Nme wa tojite ite kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,netsu wo obiru yume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:31.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Arayuru yami wo keshisaru\Nyou na kamikaze express
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,toutou hasshin desu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:39.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Negai datte mirai datte bokura wa mushiro aimai na hou ga ii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:43.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tobikata mo nanto naku de ii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:48.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kitto kitto socchi\Nno hou ga nagaku toberu ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.32,White,,0,0,0,,(ocells: piuladissa)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(Asuka) Yuichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.96,White,,0,0,0,,Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.08,White,,0,0,0,,Benvingut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.16,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.36,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Vaja!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.56,White,,0,0,0,,Em pensava que l'Asuka i aquest tal\NFukuhara només eren coneguts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Se n'haurà de buscar una altra,\NKogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.80,White,,0,0,0,,Mm! Tu calla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,És molt bona notícia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,que al final només hagi complert\Nun any de condemna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,M'imagino que l'Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,volia trobar el responsable\Nde tot plegat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,abans que en Fukuhara sortís\Nde la presó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.92,White,,0,0,0,,(Takajo) Tens raó, noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.48,White,,0,0,0,,Es veu que el senyor Fukuhara\Nhavia jurat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.76,White,,0,0,0,,que trobaria l'autèntic culpable\Nquan quedés en llibertat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:41.72,White,,0,0,0,,Però l'Asuka no estava disposada\Na permetre que corregués cap perill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:45.80,White,,0,0,0,,Llavors, dedueixo que tu coneixies fil per randa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.88,White,,0,0,0,,els plans de l'Asuka\Ndes del principi, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:51.44,White,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm. Per fi ho has descobert,\Ndetectiu de pacotilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.00,White,,0,0,0,,Ves en compte amb el que dius,\Ncarallot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:58.20,White,,0,0,0,,Vols saber qui va proposar a l'Asuka que et convidés a Yamaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Vaig ser jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:02.80,White,,0,0,0,,Li vaig dir que en Kogoro Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.36,White,,0,0,0,,el millor detectiu del Japó\Namb diferència...,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.72,White,,0,0,0,,era l'únic\Nque aconseguiria resoldre el misteri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:15.04,White,,0,0,0,,Què us sembla si anem a celebrar\Nque el cas està resolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:17.88,White,,0,0,0,,Us convido a tastar els fideus típics d'aquí, de Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.20,White,,0,0,0,,Un bon tiberi ens farà oblidar\Nles nostres diferències.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:25.04,White,,0,0,0,,Mm! Amb uns fideus no en tinc prou,\Nper fer les paus amb tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.12,White,,0,0,0,,Hi haurà barra lliure d'aiguardent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:30.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Llavors segur\Nque aviat serem bons amics.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Oh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.76,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:37.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un inspector carallot i un detectiu\Nde pacotilla..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:40.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He-he! Fan un bon equip."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:47.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja ho pots ben dir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:47.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Oh! Quin lloc més fantàstic, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:50.36,White,,0,0,0,,Ran, això em recorda alguna cosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:53.36,White,,0,0,0,,De fet, hi va haver un cas...\NQuin era?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:56.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Deu ser el cas del Mary Celeste,\Noi? Vol dir aquest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com dius? El Mary Celeste?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.08,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Oh, no pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ha desaparegut al llac...,\Nigual que els altres 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:10.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'El misteri del restaurant\Nd'una estrella'."
